Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.83,0:00:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是練馬區的農家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.41,0:00:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為明天是母親節 正為康乃馨的出貨而忙碌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.46,0:00:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家族最溫暖 溫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.17,0:00:13.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像傻瓜一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.51,0:00:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世間是沒有那麼單純的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.18,0:00:25.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真平靜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.69,0:00:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.53,0:00:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐！那個SNK-98在...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.57,0:00:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼啦！今日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.45,0:00:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今日子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.66,0:00:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,SNK-98
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.31,0:02:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近因為爸爸和媽媽都很安靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.57,0:02:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以溫子很閒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.95,0:02:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太過無敵也不是好現象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.66,0:02:45.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三島的人也不和我玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.00,0:02:52.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎？好厲害！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.58,0:02:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.71,0:02:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.26,0:03:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好貴呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.52,0:03:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨 要康乃馨嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.64,0:03:12.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不...不是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.27,0:03:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有意思 沒有意思...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.48,0:03:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.65,0:03:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在要回去嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.74,0:03:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.99,0:03:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以呀！放學途中買零食 我要去告訴爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.03,0:03:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要這樣 那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.71,0:03:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介 你要不要吃一個？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.96,0:03:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要...可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.63,0:03:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.17,0:03:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個...告訴爸爸明天... 和媽媽...好好相處...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.64,0:03:47.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請告訴他好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.01,0:03:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.31,0:03:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天一天就好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.10,0:03:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次就好 我想母親節招待媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.15,0:03:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事情很簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.40,0:04:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我辦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.28,0:04:03.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.83,0:04:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.15,0:04:39.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.96,0:05:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是三島製的機器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.18,0:05:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想吃烤魚呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.48,0:05:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請救我...我會被殺...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.80,0:05:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.17,0:05:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有辦法...一半給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.72,0:05:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.69,0:06:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.53,0:06:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.53,0:06:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏目老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.66,0:06:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.58,0:06:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 抱歉 因為連續五天沒有睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.37,0:06:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師 我是...詠美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.92,0:06:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳是詠美的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.59,0:06:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做吉川...詠美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.05,0:06:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許是吉川教授的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.47,0:06:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孫女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.85,0:06:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對對！詠美小妹！一聞始我就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.27,0:06:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教授是我學生時代的恩師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.98,0:06:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都稱呼他是生化工學之父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.15,0:06:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼教授的身體還健康嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.07,0:06:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.20,0:06:55.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？死掉啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.33,0:06:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死掉了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.41,0:07:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去年...因為實驗失敗...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.58,0:07:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祖父代替夏目老師被三島重工業雇用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.00,0:07:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開發生化機器人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.59,0:07:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是沒有辦法製出和夏目老師一樣安定的機器人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.47,0:07:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失掉了研究所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.10,0:07:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三島重工的社長們非常生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.06,0:07:24.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳爺爺應該把生化機器人的製法告訴妳了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.31,0:07:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定有告訴妳才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.02,0:07:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說著就把什麼都不知道的我監禁起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.78,0:07:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用各種方式污辱我 拷問我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.99,0:07:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳說用各種方法 是指什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.37,0:07:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這事...很不好意思說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.54,0:07:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍兒 到那邊的房間去讀書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.63,0:07:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.13,0:07:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好不容易趁機逃了出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.88,0:07:53.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽可能會這麼做嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.01,0:07:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這麼做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.05,0:07:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晶子這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.43,0:07:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一段時間沒見面墮落到如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.89,0:08:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變成無法無天的冷血女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.35,0:08:06.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像活在無明地獄徘徊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.73,0:08:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來啦！來啦！來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.15,0:08:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃燒起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.98,0:08:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧！詠美小妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.65,0:08:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以從晶子...不！從女魔王手裡把妳救出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.37,0:08:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.29,0:08:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸和平常不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.00,0:08:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連續熬夜就會變成這個樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.42,0:08:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.92,0:08:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電磁控制機器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.67,0:08:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個傢伙把抓到的機器用電磁控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.92,0:08:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管三島什麼樣的機器人來襲都不用怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.76,0:08:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是還沒有完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.81,0:08:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.81,0:08:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.02,0:08:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詠美的護衛就拜託妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.19,0:08:47.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要通宵把這做好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.81,0:08:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.19,0:08:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該早一點去睡覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.15,0:08:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我要開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.65,0:08:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天還是不行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.74,0:09:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 龍之介 我去告訴爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.95,0:09:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事...沒事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.76,0:09:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十八元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.43,0:09:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有這麼多 連康乃馨都買不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.06,0:09:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要買零食就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.22,0:09:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介可能在生氣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.94,0:09:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.40,0:09:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽的事情...說了壞話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.07,0:09:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有關係我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.08,0:09:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對的是媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.74,0:09:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 你喜歡她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.25,0:09:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好呀...有點羨慕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.55,0:09:58.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊的媽媽和爸爸呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.76,0:10:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.23,0:10:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為實驗失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.77,0:10:10.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連爸媽都？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.73,0:10:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉川家的人 代代都是因爆炸而死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.73,0:10:18.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是...不久之後...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.12,0:10:23.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉體有一天總會滅亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.49,0:10:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...我還不願意...還不願意死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.42,0:10:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有問題啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.17,0:10:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽不會殺死姊姊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.05,0:10:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介你爸爸已經不再製作機器人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.60,0:10:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.06,0:10:47.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有錢 又不想回去公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.64,0:10:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是假如你爸媽和好 回去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.61,0:10:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳有看到爸爸臉上幸福的樣子嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.82,0:10:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不可能會有這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.53,0:10:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.32,0:11:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了道歉 我買康乃馨給你好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.16,0:11:05.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用啦！買那種東西只是浪費錢而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.24,0:11:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸的名作生化機器人NK-ll24現在在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.33,0:11:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請告訴我好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.25,0:11:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要知道這件事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.50,0:11:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.43,0:11:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.89,0:11:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦 詠美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.64,0:11:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去外面被媽媽發現的話 就不得了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.81,0:11:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我們去洗澡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.86,0:11:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼突然間？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.04,0:11:52.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真舒服 詠美快來呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.54,0:11:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.71,0:12:00.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詠美 妳的褲子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.51,0:12:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屁股上面...有傷痕...用鞭子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.84,0:12:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可憐！痛嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.14,0:12:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子小姐 妳的皮膚好美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.77,0:12:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為有塗臘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.36,0:12:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同時...身材也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.95,0:12:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很想要溫子小姐的身體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.28,0:12:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃？這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.41,0:12:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想變成溫子小姐 這種身材的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.21,0:12:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭 這種事...那個地方...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.42,0:12:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙在幹嘛啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.27,0:12:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子會保護妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.33,0:13:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裡呀！應該放在這個地方才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.30,0:13:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.47,0:13:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久作！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.72,0:13:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫吉川詠美的笨女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.51,0:13:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有去...有去你那裡吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.81,0:13:39.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誌厭！為什麼這個臭女人會出現呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.02,0:13:42.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳才是！為什麼在那裡呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.98,0:13:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被NK-1124強迫誘拐來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.70,0:13:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我馬上去救妳 妳在那裡不要動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.33,0:13:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳不必來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.67,0:13:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.67,0:14:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.00,0:14:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒...沒有叫妳呀...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.09,0:14:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.84,0:14:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳在那裡做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.26,0:14:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.81,0:14:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗手間在哪裡呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.10,0:14:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭 洗手間在這邊呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.85,0:14:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.27,0:14:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.49,0:14:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊 不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.70,0:14:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.33,0:14:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳看到啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.54,0:14:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 如妳所看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.58,0:14:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是三島重工的生化機器人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.96,0:14:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.17,0:14:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼是這種命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.05,0:14:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這個漂亮的身體 有致命的缺陷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.60,0:14:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥過於激烈的話 就無法停下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.27,0:15:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久就會爆炸掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.85,0:15:06.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花的生命短暫 痛苦的事十常八九...林芙美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.07,0:15:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我想活下去 活下去想做很多的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.12,0:15:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以！NK-ll24
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.58,0:15:20.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我決定要妳的身體啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.04,0:15:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀！故意和妳一起去洗澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.34,0:15:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的就是要找到妳的停止開關在什麽地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.42,0:15:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然很可憐 溫子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.34,0:15:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不！NK-1124納命吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.27,0:15:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有在聽呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.69,0:15:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗手間在那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.65,0:15:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是生化機器人呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.86,0:15:56.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭！詠美妳這個人 請不要開玩笑呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.91,0:16:01.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳不是看到我屁股上面的記號嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.75,0:16:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是用鞭子打的傷痕嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.13,0:16:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的傷痕 用鞭子能打出來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.80,0:16:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳這傢伙真令人生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.26,0:16:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詠美小姐 妳在生什麼氣呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.05,0:16:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生氣現在才要開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.06,0:16:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳要幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.07,0:16:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,囉嗦！說也沒有用 我要上啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.49,0:16:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等...等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.09,0:16:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.51,0:16:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,納命吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.44,0:17:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詠美小姐 對不起！振作！詠美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.98,0:17:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詠美...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.04,0:17:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.50,0:17:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事 龍兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.25,0:17:31.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽出來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.67,0:17:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦！那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.43,0:17:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 龍兒 我的發明很成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.77,0:17:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！溫子！可以解開啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.44,0:17:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你雖然這麼說 我不能動呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.06,0:17:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帶走啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.74,0:18:03.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 差一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.50,0:18:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晶子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.67,0:18:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要幹什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.71,0:18:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快去追詠美小妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.05,0:18:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.59,0:18:18.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.72,0:18:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起龍兒 媽媽非常的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.10,0:18:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.73,0:18:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是...他們究竟相處很好還是不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.82,0:18:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.12,0:18:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不像龍之介是個傻瓜 想做的事情也不去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.13,0:18:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩你 很對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.00,0:18:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,P.S花浪費掉也沒關係 詠美上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.72,0:19:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快告訴我 停止開關在哪裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.77,0:19:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子不知道呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.10,0:19:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.44,0:19:14.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.94,0:19:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣啊？電擊的滋味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.24,0:19:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣把妳的頭腦燒掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.05,0:19:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.01,0:19:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詠美小妹死了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.01,0:19:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三年前和雙親一起 因實驗失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.48,0:19:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.27,0:19:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉川教授模仿詠美 製作的生化機器人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.52,0:19:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花了公司四十億圓的錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.49,0:20:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 是一個不良製品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.03,0:20:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不良製品嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.95,0:20:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.41,0:20:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.04,0:20:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是！詠美這傢伙真令人頭痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.21,0:20:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼呀！託她的福才可以這樣休息呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.30,0:20:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天不去工作的話 小姐就會囉嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.26,0:20:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果傷勢再重一點就比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.02,0:20:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳這傢伙怎麼這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.19,0:20:42.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很好嗎？阿莉莎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.32,0:20:47.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臨時新聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.62,0:20:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今早從練馬區三原台發生的謎之爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.04,0:20:55.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以後繼續燃燒 終於連豐島園也被波及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.42,0:21:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在請現場的小川記者來報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.13,0:21:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,練馬方面的目白路 因為今早的爆炸事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.26,0:21:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全癱瘓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.22,0:21:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼！爆炸？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.14,0:21:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為繼續戰鬥過於激烈的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.73,0:21:17.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這之前不收回在市內爆炸 公司信用就會有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.15,0:21:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是這種事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.32,0:21:25.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳說不良製品 我以為是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.61,0:21:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是古川教授 是一位完美主義者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.12,0:21:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.58,0:21:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不！沒有什麼 這個程度的缺陷溫子也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.72,0:21:47.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑去哪裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.93,0:21:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詠美小姐 我們停止吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.47,0:21:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住口！住口！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.06,0:21:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳的那個身體是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.20,0:22:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.83,0:22:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳還帶那種東西 放開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.21,0:22:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳這個老式的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.51,0:22:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子不會輸妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.01,0:22:36.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多應該燒掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.02,0:22:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燒掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.78,0:22:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.99,0:22:53.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詠美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.92,0:23:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有趕上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.55,0:23:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 溫子她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.10,0:23:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.61,0:23:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詠美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.32,0:23:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詠美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.41,0:23:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然這樣 我就要把你拖下水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.33,0:23:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們大家都炸掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.96,0:23:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣？ 連奔跑的迥路都控制了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.42,0:23:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是偶然呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.51,0:23:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡！不會輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.01,0:23:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我絕對要把妳的身體搶過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.43,0:23:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要如何進來我的身體裡面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.18,0:24:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我是傻爪 沒有想到這一方面的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.23,0:24:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要先把妳打倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.11,0:24:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳高興什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.90,0:24:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.44,0:24:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以後我們再一起玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.91,0:24:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧不起我 妳這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.62,0:24:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無聊！看不下去 在這麼忙的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.59,0:24:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍兒 抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:27.96,0:24:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽要回去公司 還有事情要辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.51,0:24:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.64,0:24:36.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.89,0:24:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.43,0:24:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是母親節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.64,0:24:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母親節？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:41.98,0:24:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？今天是母親節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:44.23,0:24:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！晶子 今天我請妳吃飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.32,0:24:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天...不是...四月一日吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.78,0:24:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快上車！由我來開車 龍兒你也一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.53,0:24:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:58.70,0:25:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久作 這不會是圈套吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:02.29,0:25:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭 晶子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.17,0:25:10.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對！那個機器請買下好嗎？因為花了太多的錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:10.38,0:25:14.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就看妳怎麼招待囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:15.05,0:25:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:16.59,0:25:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要理她 作為破壞城鎮的懲罰
